                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18691025-935-offence-1 t18691025-name-236"></join>Mary Newcombe</persName>, and stealing from her person one purse and a 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note, the property of <persName id="t18691025-name-237" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18691025-name-237" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18691025-name-237" type="surname" value="NEWCOMBE"></interp>
